Toshia Mori https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Toshia_Mori 0 Toshia Mori (としあ もり, January 1, 1912 – November 26, 1995) was a Japanese born actress, who had a brief career in American films during the 1930s. Born as Toshiye Ichioka (としいぇ いちおか ) in Kyoto, Mori moved to the United States when she was ten years old.
